com.ibm.jaggr.core.resource

Interface IResourceConverterExtensionPoint


  • public interface IResourceConverterExtensionPoint
    This interface defines constants for the resourceconverter extension point

    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static String ID
      Name extension point id.
      static Class<?> INTERFACE
      A reference to the IResourceConverter interface which is the interface that plugin extensions of the resourceconverter extension point must implement.
      static String NAME
      The extension point name.
      static String NAMESPACE
      The extension point namespace.
      static String[] REQUIRED_ATTRIBUTES
      List of required extension attributes for the resourceconverter extension point.

    • Field Detail

      • NAME

        static final String NAME
        The extension point name. This value is combined with the namespace for the extension point to form the extension point id.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • NAMESPACE

        static final String NAMESPACE
        The extension point namespace. This value is combined with the extension point name to form the extension point id.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • ID

        static final String ID
        Name extension point id. This is the combination of the extension point namespace plus the extension point name.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • REQUIRED_ATTRIBUTES

        static final String[] REQUIRED_ATTRIBUTES
        List of required extension attributes for the resourceconverter extension point.

      • INTERFACE

        static final Class<?> INTERFACE
        A reference to the IResourceConverter interface which is the interface that plugin extensions of the resourceconverter extension point must implement.
